cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC. 

This paper discusses the development of a DSL editor, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL) categories. The use of a generation tool and compositional language definition features also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the importance of a comfortable editor for user acceptance implies a consideration of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
